CREATE TABLE categories (category_id INT PRIMARY KEY, category_name STRING, parent_category_id INT REFERENCES categories(category_id))</t><stat>INSERT INTO accounts (account_id, user_id, account_type, balance) SELECT 1, 1, 'Savings', 1000.00</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE accounts (account_id INT PRIMARY KEY, user_id INT REFERENCES users(id), account_type STRING, balance DECIMAL(10, 2))
